A fundraiser for the Souris River Recreation Commission well be held at the Wawanesa Community Hall on Friday. 
The commission operates the Wawanesa waterpark and campground and the Wawanesa Baseball Park as well as providing activities in Wawanesa and the surrounding area. Please subscribe to view full article.
